@NODE "Introduction" "Introduction"
@WORDWRAP
WinBack III restores backup-files made with Windows Backup.

WinBack III gives you a nice MUI-gui where you can select which files to restore from the backup-sett.
 
WinBack III is tested with DD(720k) and HD(1.44M) disks and backups from Windows 95 & Windows 98.
I haven't had an opportunity to test it with backups from Windows NT, so I don't know if the standards are different, e-mail me...
@ENDNODE
